const items = $input.all();
const agents = items[0]?.json || {};
const workflows = items[1]?.json || {};
const infra = items[2]?.json || {};
const incidents = items[3]?.json || {};
const mindex = items[4]?.json || {};

const weekEnd = new Date();
const weekStart = new Date(Date.now() - 7 * 86400000);

const report = {
  title: `MYCA Weekly Operations Report`,
  period: `${weekStart.toISOString().split('T')[0]} to ${weekEnd.toISOString().split('T')[0]}`,
  generated: new Date().toISOString(),

  executive_summary: {
    agents_active: agents.active_count || 0,
    total_tasks_processed: agents.total_tasks || 0,
    avg_success_rate: agents.avg_success_rate || 0,
    workflow_executions: workflows.total_executions || 0,
    workflow_success_rate: workflows.success_rate || 0,
    incidents_total: (incidents.alerts || []).length,
    incidents_critical: (incidents.alerts || []).filter(a => a.severity === 'critical').length,
    uptime_pct: infra.avg_uptime_pct || 99.9
  },

  agent_performance: {
    total_agents: agents.total || 0,
    most_active: agents.top_performers || [],
    categories: agents.by_category || {},
    tasks_by_day: agents.daily_breakdown || []
  },

  infrastructure: {
    avg_cpu: infra.avg_cpu || 0,
    avg_memory: infra.avg_memory || 0,
    disk_growth_gb: infra.disk_growth_gb || 0,
    vm_status: infra.vm_status || {},
    backup_status: infra.backup_status || 'unknown'
  },

  data_growth: {
    new_species: mindex.new_species || 0,
    new_records: mindex.new_records || 0,
    vector_count: mindex.vector_count || 0,
    knowledge_nodes: mindex.knowledge_nodes || 0
  },

  incidents_summary: {
    total: (incidents.alerts || []).length,
    by_severity: {},
    top_issues: (incidents.alerts || []).slice(0, 5).map(a => ({
      title: a.title,
      severity: a.severity,
      time: a.timestamp
    }))
  }
};

// Count by severity
for (const alert of (incidents.alerts || [])) {
  const sev = alert.severity || 'unknown';
  report.incidents_summary.by_severity[sev] = (report.incidents_summary.by_severity[sev] || 0) + 1;
}

return [{ json: report }];
